</svg>                        Generate presentation                    </span>
                    <span x-show="openFromTemplate" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
                        <svg class="size-4 shrink-0 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
